code: /**  * A series of global options as key value pairs  */ public void setGlobalOptions(List<GlobalOptionDefinition> globalOptions) {     this.globalOptions = globalOptions. }
public Map<String, String> asMap() {     return getGlobalOptions().stream().collect(Collectors.toMap(o -> o.getKey(), o -> o.getValue(), (o1, o2) -> o2)). }
